cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

The paper proposes a deep learning approach for image reconstruction, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of a convolutional autoencoder and backpropagation also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). The application of the algorithm to medical imaging may also suggest a connection to multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the use of multiple decoders with random initializations and selection during training may suggest a connection to neural networks (cs.NE).
